  div.container
    h1.heading A Timestamp Microservice
    div.box
      h2.heading Description
      div.text-block
        p.text This service provides time in both <b>natural</b> and <b>unix</b> formats. <br /><br /><b>The natural format</b> is the time as written in english language, in the form of: DD Month, YYYY.<br /><br /><b>The unix format</b> (also known as POSIX time or epoch time) denotes the number of seconds that have elapsed since 00:00:00 Coordinated Universal Time (UTC), Thursday, 1 January 1970, not counting leap seconds.<br /><br /><b>Simply pass the time in a natural or unix format on the tail end of this url!</b>
      
      h2.heading Example API Calls
      div.text-block
        p.code https://timestamps.glitch.me/April%2013,%202017<br /><br />
        p.code https://timestamps.glitch.me/1492041600
      h2.heading Example Output
      div.text-block
        p.code {"unix":1492041600,"natural":"April 13, 2017"}
      h2.heading The Current Epoch Time is...
        p#epoch
        
